contracts\README.md:130:| operationId | HTTP 入口 | Requirement IDs | 后续 handler | DB / worker / audit / file 追踪要求 | 后续测试映射 |
contracts\README.md:132:| `createExportTask` | `POST /api/export/tasks` | FR-001 / FR-009 / FR-013 | `src/routes/export/tasks/create-export-task.handler.ts` | DB: task、idempotency、registry、audit；worker: 消费已提交 `PENDING`；audit: `CREATE` | contract / api / db |
contracts\README.md:133:| `listExportTasks` | `GET /api/export/tasks` | FR-004 / FR-009 / FR-010 | `src/routes/export/tasks/list-export-tasks.handler.ts` | DB: task、file、audit；audit: `QUERY_HISTORY`；file: 只返回已发布文件元信息 | contract / api |
contracts\README.md:134:| `getExportTask` | `GET /api/export/tasks/{taskId}` | FR-002 / FR-010 / FR-013 | `src/routes/export/tasks/get-export-task.handler.ts` | DB: task、event、attempt、file；worker: checkpoint / lease 证据；audit: `DETAIL_VIEW` | contract / api |
contracts\README.md:135:| `downloadExportTask` | `GET /api/export/tasks/{taskId}/download` | FR-003 / FR-009 / FR-010 | `src/routes/export/tasks/download-export-task.handler.ts` | DB: task、file、audit；file: published object、checksum、expiry、delivery mode；audit: `DOWNLOAD` | contract / file |
contracts\README.md:136:| `cancelExportTask` | `POST /api/export/tasks/{taskId}/cancel` | FR-012 / FR-010 | `src/routes/export/tasks/cancel-export-task.handler.ts` | DB: task、event、audit；worker: EXECUTING 批次边界收口；audit: cancel request/done | contract / worker |
contracts\README.md:137:| `retryExportTask` | `POST /api/export/tasks/{taskId}/retry` | FR-012 / FR-013 / FR-010 | `src/routes/export/tasks/retry-export-task.handler.ts` | DB: task、attempt、event、audit；worker: 仅 FAILED 入队新尝试；audit: retry request | contract / db |
contracts\README.md:138:| `createExportRegistry` | `POST /api/export/registries` | FR-007 / FR-008 / FR-009 | `src/routes/export/registries/create-export-registry.handler.ts` | DB: registry、registry version、audit；query: schema/template/mapping/masking snapshot；audit: `REGISTRY_CREATE` | contract / api |
contracts\README.md:139:| `listExportRegistries` | `GET /api/export/registries` | FR-007 / FR-008 / FR-009 | `src/routes/export/registries/list-export-registries.handler.ts` | DB: registry、registry version；audit: `REGISTRY_QUERY` | contract |
contracts\README.md:140:| `getExportRegistry` | `GET /api/export/registries/{taskCode}` | FR-007 / FR-008 / FR-013 | `src/routes/export/registries/get-export-registry.handler.ts` | DB: registry、registry version；snapshot digest 必须可追溯；audit: `REGISTRY_DETAIL` | contract |
contracts\README.md:141:| `updateExportRegistry` | `PUT /api/export/registries/{taskCode}` | FR-007 / FR-008 / FR-013 | `src/routes/export/registries/update-export-registry.handler.ts` | DB: registry、registry version、audit；worker/query: 更新只影响新任务，旧任务继续使用快照；audit: `REGISTRY_UPDATE` | contract / db |
contracts\README.md:142:| `enableExportRegistry` | `POST /api/export/registries/{taskCode}/enable` | FR-007 | `src/routes/export/registries/enable-export-registry.handler.ts` | DB: registry、audit；audit: `REGISTRY_ENABLE` | contract |
contracts\README.md:143:| `disableExportRegistry` | `POST /api/export/registries/{taskCode}/disable` | FR-007 | `src/routes/export/registries/disable-export-registry.handler.ts` | DB: registry、audit；后续创建必须返回 `TASK_DISABLED`；audit: `REGISTRY_DISABLE` | contract |
contracts\README.md:154:4. API 契约、scheduler 契约、query 契约、file 契约、audit 契约和 sample 契约必须保持同一组术语，尤其是 `attemptNo`、`configSnapshotDigest`、`batchCheckpoint`、`storageKey`、`requestId`。
contracts\README.md:156:6. query 契约必须明确禁止原始 SQL，只允许参数化模板和参数 schema 绑定。
contracts\README.md:165:| Query 契约 | `*.md` 或 `*.schema.json` | `contracts/query/template-and-mapping.md` |
contracts\README.md:166:| File 契约 | `*.md` | `contracts/file/publish-and-download.md` |
contracts\README.md:167:| Audit 契约 | `*.md` | `contracts/audit/task-events.md` |
contracts\README.md:168:| Sample 契约 | `*.md` | `contracts/sample/purchase-order-export.md` |
contracts\README.md:173:2. 再按 `api/`、`scheduler/`、`query/`、`file/`、`audit/`、`sample/` 分区补齐契约说明。
